- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with spoken language understanding and natural language processing techniques. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper focuses on extracting semantic concepts directly from speech audio signals. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a transfer learning strategy based on the principles of curriculum learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper presents an end-to-end approach for spoken language understanding. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing speech audio signals.
